flowchart LR
    accTitle: PR 387 warm-pool data flow before and after the agent-sandbox upgrade
    accDescr: The old v0.1.1 path adopts a pre-warmed Pod and creates a Sandbox with the Claim name. The new v0.4.6 path adopts a pre-warmed Sandbox with a different runtime identity, publishes that name through Claim status, and preserves the Claim identity in Store for deletion.

    subgraph BEFORE["更新前 | v0.1.1 | 按【差异 1-7】横向对照"]
        direction TB
        B_REQ["<b>共同流程</b><br/>Client / SDK 创建 session"]:::source
        B_WM["<b>共同流程</b><br/>WorkloadManager 创建 SandboxClaim"]:::process
        B_POOL["<b>差异 1｜池化对象</b><br/>SandboxWarmPool 直接维护<br/><b>Pod</b>"]:::controller
        B_ADOPT["<b>差异 2｜adopt 对象</b><br/>adopt <b>预热 Pod</b><br/>另建同名 Sandbox"]:::controller
        B_IDENTITY["<b>差异 3｜身份关系</b><br/><b>Claim.name = Sandbox.name</b><br/>annotation 指向 adopted Pod"]:::runtime
        B_READY["<b>差异 4｜就绪发现</b><br/>预注册同名 Sandbox watcher<br/>informer Ready event 驱动"]:::legacy
        B_POD["<b>差异 5｜Pod 读取</b><br/>annotation → informer cache<br/>读取 Pod IP + 探测端口"]:::runtime
        B_STORE[("<b>差异 6｜Store 身份</b><br/>Name = Claim = Sandbox<br/>控制/运行名称自然重合")]:::state
        B_DELETE["<b>共同动作</b>：Delete / GC 删除 Claim<br/><b>差异 7｜补池对象</b><br/>新建 replacement <b>Pod</b>"]:::lifecycle

        B_REQ -->|create session| B_WM
        B_WM -->|create Claim| B_ADOPT
        B_POOL -.->|提供 ready Pod| B_ADOPT
        B_ADOPT -->|same-name contract| B_IDENTITY
        B_IDENTITY -->|同名 Ready event| B_READY
        B_WM -.->|预注册 watcher| B_READY
        B_READY -->|Ready Sandbox| B_POD
        B_POD -->|runtime fields| B_STORE
        B_STORE -->|按 Claim identity| B_DELETE
    end

    subgraph AFTER["更新后 | PR #387 + v0.4.6 | 看右侧同编号"]
        direction TB
        A_REQ["<b>共同流程</b><br/>Client / SDK 创建 session"]:::source
        A_WM["<b>共同流程</b><br/>WorkloadManager 创建 SandboxClaim"]:::process
        A_POOL["<b>差异 1｜池化对象</b><br/>SandboxWarmPool 维护<br/><b>Sandbox → Pod</b>"]:::controller
        A_ADOPT["<b>差异 2｜adopt 对象</b><br/>adopt <b>预热 Sandbox</b><br/>owner: Pool → Claim；名称 / UID 不变"]:::controller
        A_IDENTITY["<b>差异 3｜身份关系</b><br/><b>Claim.name ≠ Sandbox.name</b><br/>status.sandbox.name 建立桥接"]:::runtime
        A_READY["<b>差异 4｜就绪发现</b><br/>live GET Claim → Sandbox<br/>检查 Sandbox Ready；2m context 覆盖两次 GET"]:::process
        A_POD["<b>差异 5｜Pod 读取</b><br/>annotation / 默认名 → live GET Pod<br/>读取 Pod IP + 探测端口"]:::runtime
        A_STORE[("<b>差异 6｜Store 身份</b><br/>控制身份：Kind / Name = Claim<br/>运行身份：Sandbox UID / Pod EntryPoints")]:::state
        A_DELETE["<b>共同动作</b>：Delete / GC 删除 Claim<br/><b>差异 7｜补池对象</b><br/>新建 replacement <b>Sandbox → Pod</b>"]:::lifecycle

        A_REQ -->|create session| A_WM
        A_WM -->|create Claim| A_ADOPT
        A_POOL -.->|选择 ready Sandbox| A_ADOPT
        A_ADOPT -.->|发布 runtime 名称| A_IDENTITY
        A_IDENTITY -->|status.sandbox.name| A_READY
        A_READY -->|adopted Sandbox| A_POD
        A_POD -->|runtime fields| A_STORE
        A_STORE -->|按 Claim identity| A_DELETE
    end

    B_REQ ~~~ A_REQ

